des: List of vegetarian and vegan restaurant options in Boston. Includes addresses, phone number, and brief descriptions which can be heard from Alexa, and read in the companion Alexa app. To enable, say "Alexa, enable Boston Vegan." Then to use, simply say, "Alexa, ask Boston Vegan for a fact."
